To compile Elastic Droid using Ant, you must specify where your Android SDK is via the local.properties file. 

sdk.dir=/path/to/android/sdk

To set your development environment up, please see http://code.google.com/p/elastic-droid/wiki/DevEnvironmentSetup

For information on this program, please contact Siddhu Warrier at siddhu AT siddhuw DOT info.